rows.label: tlk400901_msg0001
rows.name: Huh? You're...Periperi, right?

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0002
rows.name:
Ahhh! Rex!
Such coincidence to meet here!

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0003
rows.name:
You haven't brought any cargo
from Gula, have you?

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0004
rows.name: Have so.

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0005
rows.name: Even though you were in Avaritia?

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0006
rows.name:
Came from Avaritia to Gula,
then Gula to Superbia!

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0007
rows.name: Oh, I see... I guess that makes sense.

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0008
rows.name:
Then Tora have something
to ask Periperi.

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0009
rows.name:
Did Periperi transport large quantity
of Bion Connector recently?

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0010
rows.name:
Mo-mo-mo!
Talking about contents of shipment
is violation of trade confidentiality!

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0011
rows.name: Come on, we really need to know this.

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0012
rows.name:
Ahhhhh... If it request from Rex,
Periperi can not refuse!

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0013
rows.name:
Periperi carried Bion Connector
in yellow barrels.

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0014
rows.name: How many?

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0015
rows.name: At least 10, Periperi think.

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0016
rows.name: That's got to be it.

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0017
rows.name: Periperi know where shipment for?

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0018
rows.name:
Sadly not having that information.
Job was only bring cargo to port.

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0019
rows.name:
But cargo unloaded here always
taken off towards city.

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0020
rows.name:
Maybe friends find cargo at inspection
point near elevator. Only if recipient
not pick up yet, of course.

rows.label: tlk400901_msg0021
rows.name:
All right, we'll have a look.
Thanks, Periperi.
